STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Dennis OBADO, a/k/a Dennis Abado, Defendant-Movant. M-429 September Term 2017
079196 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 8, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion to vacate the order of dismissal and reinstate the notice of petition for certification is denied.
